veral projects at once Must submit a cover letter with resume Marketing Director Unpakt is seeking a full-time Marketing Director to work closely with all departments to execute Unpaktâ\u0080\u0099s strategic marketing plan, partnerships, affiliate, social media, and PR. We are looking for a creative, execution-oriented Marketing Director who can put Unpakt on the map. You will own the marketing domain for our startup, whether online or offline efforts. Your focus will be to expand and deepen penetration to main cities around the country. Your range of work might cover a lot of ground, and you will often need to be scrappy and self-sufficient, but we also have the financial resources to bring in external resources or scale up investment as justified. You will have a lot of freedom to experiment to see what works, but will also need to be diligent about investing time and money in the ideas delivering the best results. Job Description: Design and organize creative offline and online marketing campaigns Be comfortable both executing work directly and managing vendors to help produce campaigns Assess, cultivate, and implement strategic partnerships Execute the strategies, plans and development of the Affiliate Program Run and optimize AdWords campaigns Manage content generation and distribution Work with PR agency on all public relations activities to generate greater brand awareness for Unpakt Lead our social media presence and related content strategy Own all aspects of Vendor Marketing (marketing to our movers partners/merchants) Requirements: Bachelorâ\u0080\u0099s Degree or greater 3+ years marketing experience Hands-on experience with SEO and SEM best practices Experience with Google Analytics Ability to interact effectively with various constituents at a company including C-level leaders Demonstrate ability to manage relationships and partnerships with individuals, organizations, and communities Startup experience a plus Excellent communication and writing skills Highly-motivated and entrepreneurial BlogFor moversPressCareersDeals©Unpakt LLC 20131-855-2UNPAKTPrivacy policyTermsMade with ♥ in NYCUnpakt is a SupplierMember of the AmericanMoving & Storage AssociationWhat we doHow it worksFor moversBlogCompanyAbout Unpakt/1/about-unpaktCareersPressDealsNeed help?FAQContacthttps://www.unpakt.com/contactConnectFacebookTwitterGoogle+YouTube©Unpakt LLC 20131-855-2UNPAKTPrivacy policyTermsMade with ♥ in NYCUnpakt is a Supplier Member of theAmerican Moving & Storage Associationpowered by", is_draft: true, company_id: 957, dept: "Engineering", years_exp: 2, key_skill_one: "Rails", key_skill_two: "Javascript", sub_dept: "Back-End", description: "As one of our senior developers, you love working in an agile environment, want to solve a real-world problem with a large market potential, and know how to write maintainable code. "},
