 we offer many perks to help you maintain that important work-life balance, such as complimentary yoga and the chance to enjoy socializing with your coworkers during our weekly catered lunches. Read on and learn about more of the beautiful reasons to work at 1stdibs. This is an amazing opportunity to rebuild a high volume online marketplace. We are planning on a complete architecture overhaul. Databases will be redesigned, hardware will be revamped, web stack replaced, caching layers implemented. You will have the opportunity to build something exciting and new with the guarantee that your work will be seen by a strong and rapidly growing, global online community of dealers and consumers including antique dealers, interior designers and collectors. Some of what you’ll do… Contribute to a small team designing and developing a services platform Leverage caching, messaging and asynchronous processing Contribute to the design of a new database schema Implement an end-to-end ecommerce solutions Analyze and assess business requirements, choose the right tools and libraries to implement solutions Work closely with a fantastic Product organization to envision and create solutions that delight our existing customer and attract many new ones About you… Love the util.concurrent package Ability to bring your intellectual curiosity and thoughtful opinions with you everyday. Be awesome and make those around you awesome! Experience developing consumer-facing websites in professional production environment a plus Experience Developing code for high-traffic web sites Able to troubleshoot and explain performance bottlenecks Know that mule and tomcat aren’t just animal names An appreciation for one-of-a-kind items such as furniture, art and jewelry always welcome Your participation in the larger Developer Community is strongly supported and encouraged! APPLY All Positions Marketplace Support Specialist Interaction Designer Photographer - Atlanta Visual Web Designer Accounting Operations Manager Director, Analytics Graphic Designer Web Analyst (Part-Time) Front-End Engineer (JavaScript, HTML, CSS) Mobile Architect Extras Summer Fridays Weekly White Linen Lunches Snacks Full Benefits & 401k Paid Family Leave Commuter Benefits In-Office Yoga SHARE: FOLLOW US: twitter facebook pinterest About Us Support Center Contact Us Careers Press Privacy Site Map Dealer Login", is_draft: true, company_id: 6, dept: "Engineering", years_exp: 1, key_skill_one: "Java", key_skill_two: nil, sub_dept: "Back-End", description: nil},
