  {link: "https://adstruc.com/s/home/jobs/director-engineering", title: "Director of Engineering", full_text: "Login Forgot your password? Login I am a: Agency Advertiser Operator « Back to jobs Director of Engineering Location: NYC Department: Engineering Type: Full Time We Are Looking For: ADstruc seeks an experienced Director of Engineering to lead its software engineering team, oversee the design and architecture of its flagship media-buying platform, and continuously prepare it for growth. Responsibilities: Lead a small team of software engineers in a startup environment Manage the performance of your team, helping them become even better engineers and grow in their careers Spend 25-50% of your time hands-on, working on everything from backend and user-interface to database systems and third-party integrations Work alongside product management to evolve the team’s agile development process and foster a positive and results-driven engineering culture Manage the availability and performance of all environments, continuously fixing bottlenecks and planning for growth Occasionally attend client meetings and participate in business discussions where strategy and technology intersect Lead the hiring of all future software engineers Requirements: 5-7 years of software engineering experience with 2+ years in a leadership role Experience developing web applications with agile methodologies Excellent coding, design, and architectural skills (PHP, SQL, Linux) A record of successful contributions to a productive engineering culture Experience managing environments, scaling web applications, and using monitoring tools (e.g. Nagios, Zabbix) Strong interpersonal communication skills and experience interfacing with clients A college degree from a Computer Science program Benefits: Apple equipment Competitive salary Health, dental and vision insurance Stock options Team outings, including volunteering at various charities Great SoHo office space Free ping pong lessons We Are: A